RT @Lovinglyraj: @Jharrisjayaraj ,WHEN u do sonG likANJALA MACHAN ANJALAI .

One is on the way in the upcoming album" 7 Aam arrive".

name: Harris Jayaraj
text:
RT @Athinivas: @Jharrisjayaraj r u really doing the remake of kaakha kaakha film sir ???              

Yes athinivas.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Back from singapore after composing hand full of tunes for the film "7 aam arivu". Looking forward to record.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Praise the lord. Felt nice receiving 3 trophies for music in 4th vijay awards. Thanks to all my musicians, singers and my fans.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Just came back from the composing session of the Hindi kaakha kaakha . Gave a nostalgia feeling after 9 years.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text:
Jharrisjayaraj 
  
Congratulations to the men in Yellow and the fans of "Chennai Super Kings" for scooping this year IPL League Trophy.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: The challenging part is that we've planned to come up with fresh tunes for all songs except the track "Uyirin Uyirae".

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Hi.. Signed the hindi version of "Kaakha Kaakha" yesterday, which is going to be directed by "Nishikant Kamath" and produced by Vipul Shah.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Liked the song "Aval Appadivondrum Azhaghiyillay" from "Angaadi theru".

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Saw the film "Angaadi theru" today and would like to congratulate the entire team for coming up with a brilliant movie.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Met my long time friend after a long time in my studio today. Let's see how this new bond take us from now !

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: i've come to bangalore to start the new film with A.R.Murugadoss... wish all remember in your prayers. Thank you

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Hi guys, My second appearance on stage today for a song to be performed at nehru stadium. Come and join...

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Just finished the song "Vaa Vaa Thalaiva ". Sung by 10 singers will be performed on 6th before CM.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Congratulations to A.R.Rahman and his fans for winning 2 grammy awards and i wish more to come.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Vaaranam Aayiram has won the "Best Film of 2008"  National award. I would like to thank the Almighty and fans for making this possible.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Have been asked to compose a song on CM written by Mr Vaali and that will be sung by all the stars of the tamil industry on 6th of Feb.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Happy pongal. Back to chennai from china and macau yesterday. Shall start working on the songs of "Ko".

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Happy going 2nd week... Like to thank everyone who had wished and blessed me on my birthday. Luv u all.

name: Harris Jayaraj
text: Celebrated my birthday in a soft and cold environment at macau. It's so nice to compose the songs of "Ko" on the same day. Love u all.
